<hl>
<seg id=1> China will speed up the system construction of the human resource market. </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, 1 September The Ministry of Organization and the Ministry of Personnel of the CPC Central Committee sent out a notice recently on enhancing the constructive plan of the construction of the human resource market, speeding up the process of it and promoting its healthy development. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> According to the notice, the overall target of the development of the human resource market was that individuals had the freedom to choose their own profession; work units had the freedom to employ their employees; the market would adjust the relation between supply and demand; the social service should be perfect; the social insurance should be strengthened; under the macro-adjustment and control of the government, the market should play a foundational role on the adjustment of human resources. </seg>
<seg id=4> The short-term targets of the development of the human resource market were to formulate the basic policies and regulations of the operation of the market in 2 to 3 years, set up the places of the human resource market in big and medium-sized cities, build and improve the network of human resources, support the development of the market of experts and build regional markets. </seg>
<seg id=5> Before 2000, we should preliminarily establish the system of the human resource market with perfect functions and mechanism, a complete set of rules and regulations, instant guidance and good service. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> The Ministry of Organization and the Ministry of Personnel of the CPC Central Committee asked all level personnel departments to improve the construction and administration of the human resource market, develop the research and planning of the market, establish the overall arrangement and measures, suit measures to local conditions, provide classified instructions, and perfect the system gradually. </seg>
</p>
